THROUGH THE REST OF THE AFTERNOON WITH SEAS 5 FEET NEAR SHORE TO
15 FEET OFFSHORE. WINDS AND SEAS SHOULD BEGIN TO DIMINISH
OVERNIGHT.

...NEXT UPDATE...

